21
00:01:19,260 --> 00:01:21,790
But slaves aren't people.

22
00:01:21,790 --> 00:01:24,340
Training one is no different than upgrading my shield.

23
00:01:25,360 --> 00:01:28,200
Well, you've got me there.

24
00:01:29,170 --> 00:01:33,500
