Probably because you set her as acompanion when forming the pact.

80
00:06:13,350 --> 00:06:16,930
Wait, you didn't do thatwith the lady from before?

81
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:19,020
Damn that woman...

82
00:06:19,780 --> 00:06:20,480
Listen up.

83
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:25,780
From here on out, I expect you to fight monsters for me.

84
00:06:27,110 --> 00:06:29,200
