151
00:09:47,980 --> 00:09:49,730
And then, the one with the shield!

152
00:09:50,020 --> 00:09:50,940
Correct.

153
00:09:50,940 --> 00:09:56,240
The Shield Hero, in particular, treated us demi-humans very well.

154
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:59,200
Really? I'd like to meet him.

155
00:09:59,490 --> 00:10:02,830
If you're a good girl, I'm sure you'll meet him one day.

156
00:10:09,380 --> 00:10:12,340
The Shield Hero...

157
00:10:12,340 --> 00:10:14,760
U-Um... What is your name?

158
00:10:15,260 --> 00:10:16,840
Iwatani Naofumi.

159
00:10:17,170 --> 00:10:19,800
Iwatani... Naofumi.

160
00:10:21,890 --> 00:10:23,300
Drink this.

161
00:10:24,850 --> 00:10:26,730
It's a medicine I blended.

162
00:10:26,730 --> 00:10:28,520
Apparently, it can cure mild colds.

163
00:10:29,270 --> 00:10:30,350
Drink it.

164
00:10:35,650 --> 00:10:36,690
So bitter!

165
00:10:36,690 --> 00:10:38,950
Good medicine tastes bitter.

166
00:10:38,950 --> 00:10:39,820
Just drink it all.

167
