205
00:12:50,370 --> 00:12:52,250
You will let us stay, right?

206
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:55,790
O-Of course! I'll prepare a room at once!

207
00:12:59,420 --> 00:13:04,340
I have to find a way to survive before the next Wave of Catastrophe hits.

208
00:13:37,790 --> 00:13:41,340
All right. We can go a little deeper into the forest now...

209
00:13:45,340 --> 00:13:46,880
A rabbit?

210
00:13:47,470 --> 00:13:48,220
Watch out!

211
00:13:49,350 --> 00:13:51,390
Now, Raphtalia! Stab it!

212
00:13:53,350 --> 00:13:55,430
What's wrong? Get on with it!

213
00:13:55,430 --> 00:13:58,600
B-But... It'll bleed if I do...

214
00:13:58,600 --> 00:13:59,650
Hurry up!

215
00:13:59,650 --> 00:14:01,390
I'm scared of blood!

216
00:14:05,150 --> 00:14:06,990
Listen well.

217
00:14:07,280 --> 00:14:10,700
If you can't fight, then I won't be able to look after you anymore.

218
00:14:12,790 --> 00:14:15,370
A Wave that threatens the world's existence is coming soon.

219
00:14:15,370 --> 00:14:18,540
I have to get as strong as I can before it does.

220
00:14:18,960 --> 00:14:21,880
But defense is all I'm good for.

221
00:14:21,880 --> 00:14:24,340
I need someone to fight for me.

222
00:14:25,050 --> 00:14:27,680
If you can't do it, I'll get someone else.

223
00:14:29,390 --> 00:14:30,260
So...

224
00:14:30,260 --> 00:14:32,890
You're going to fight the Catastrophe?

225
00:14:32,890 --> 00:14:34,640
That is my job.

226
00:14:36,140 --> 00:14:37,350
Got it.

227
00:14:50,860 --> 00:14:54,830
Master... I'll fight for you.

228
00:14:55,290 --> 00:14:58,000
So please don't throw me away.

229
00:14:58,660 --> 00:14:59,580
All right.

230
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:02,580
This is reality.

231
00:15:03,210 --> 00:15:04,460
Not a game.

232
00:15:04,800 --> 00:15:08,010
If I want to live, I have no choice but to fight!

233
00:15:10,590 --> 00:15:12,390
Sell us a new weapon for this amount.

234
00:15:12,640 --> 00:15:16,600
Time to get the little miss a sword, then.

235
00:15:18,350 --> 00:15:20,940
One on the short side would be good to start off.

236
00:15:21,310 --> 00:15:22,730
How about this?

237
